name: Texas Chicken (The Seletar Mall)

reviews.text: I hate you guys for giving me breast meat, along with my $24 order on GrabFood, which clearly shows a drumstick and a wrap. No other fried chicken fast food chain would do that. I can understand if I had ordered more than two pieces of chicken, but I only ordered one and I expected it to be a drumstick because there are people that do not eat breast meat.
Order an ala carte Mac & Cheese for my kid and surprisingly when I opened up are just half a cup or looks like someone ate half! How come will just gave me half a cup at $3? So disappointing!

Good food in general, but the soy garlic chicken falls short of expectations. Taste was bland and not flavourful like the usual Korean fried chicken.

Remaining food was good. Restaurant is clean and spacious.

This is the Worst Chicken I ever had. The chicken are cold and dry. The cold straw are smelly not fresh. The  The chicken are cold and dry. The cold straw are smelly not fresh. The French fries hard n cold. Tea cold as well smell bad like left over last night just add water on it. is bad. Disappointed. Will never go again. No wonder Sunday  no customer in the outlet.

Friend chicken waa good.
I have tried popcorn would not even give one star.
Cold drink was good with some different flavour.
Service was good as well
